<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Legal Notice</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .sender-info {
            max-width: 320px;
        }

        .sender-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .sender-detail {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .doc-badge {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #dc2626;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        }

        .doc-date {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .doc-date strong {
            color: #111827;
        }

        .urgency-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            background: #fef2f2;
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .via-section {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #991b1b;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .recipient {
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .recipient-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .recipient-addr {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .subject {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #991b1b;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.8;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .facts-section {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .facts-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .facts-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .demand-section {
            background: #fffbeb;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .demand-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .demand-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .demand-list li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #78350f;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .consequence-box {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .consequence-box h4 {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #991b1b;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .consequence-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #7f1d1d;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .deadline-box {
            background: #111827;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .deadline-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #f9fafb;
        }

        .deadline-sub {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .sig-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            padding-top: 8px;
            width: 280px;
        }

        .sig-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .sig-role {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .cc-section {
            margin-top: 32px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .cc-section strong {
            color: #111827;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="sender-info">
            <div class="sender-name">{{senderName}}</div>
            <div class="sender-detail">{{{senderAddress}}}</div>
            {{#if senderPhone}}<div class="sender-detail">Phone: {{senderPhone}}</div>{{/if}}
            {{#if senderEmail}}<div class="sender-detail">Email: {{senderEmail}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="doc-badge">
            <div class="doc-title">LEGAL NOTICE</div>
            <div class="doc-date"><strong>Date:</strong> {{noticeDate}}</div>
            {{#if refNumber}}<div class="doc-date"><strong>Ref:</strong> {{refNumber}}</div>{{/if}}
            <div class="urgency-badge">Urgent & Confidential</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="via-section">Sent via Registered Post / Speed Post A.D. / Email</div>

    <div class="recipient">
        <div class="section-label">To</div>
        <div class="recipient-name">{{recipientName}}</div>
        <div class="recipient-addr">{{{recipientAddress}}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="subject">Subject: {{noticeSubject}}</div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{recipientName}},</p>

        <p>Under the instructions and on behalf of my client <strong>{{#if
                clientName}}{{clientName}}{{else}}{{senderName}}{{/if}}</strong>, I hereby serve upon you this Legal
            Notice as follows:</p>

        <div class="facts-section">
            <div class="facts-title">Statement of Facts</div>
            <div class="facts-text">{{{noticeDescription}}}</div>
        </div>

        <p>The above-mentioned acts/omissions on your part constitute a clear violation of the legal rights of my client
            and are actionable under the applicable laws of India.</p>

        <div class="demand-section">
            <div class="demand-title">Demands</div>
            <ol class="demand-list">
                <li>You are hereby called upon to {{#if demandAction}}{{{demandAction}}}{{else}}immediately cease and
                    desist from the above-mentioned acts and compensate my client for the damages suffered{{/if}}.</li>
                <li>You are further required to provide a written undertaking that such acts shall not be repeated in
                    the future.</li>
                <li>Failing compliance with the above demands, my client shall be constrained to initiate appropriate
                    civil and/or criminal proceedings against you, at your risk, cost, and consequences.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="deadline-box">
            <div class="deadline-text">Response Deadline: {{#if responseDeadline}}{{responseDeadline}}{{else}}15 days
                from receipt of this notice{{/if}}</div>
            <div class="deadline-sub">Failure to respond will result in legal proceedings without further notice</div>
        </div>

        <div class="consequence-box">
            <h4>Legal Consequences</h4>
            <p>Please note that if you fail to comply with the demands stated herein within the stipulated time, my
                client shall be compelled to initiate appropriate legal proceedings before the competent
                court/tribunal/authority, including but not limited to filing a civil suit for recovery of damages,
                injunction, and/or criminal complaint as may be warranted by the circumstances. All costs, charges, and
                consequences of such proceedings shall be entirely at your risk and expense.</p>
        </div>

        <p>This notice is issued without prejudice to any other rights, claims, or remedies that my client may have
            under law, all of which are expressly reserved.</p>

        <p>A copy of this notice is retained for record and future reference.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="sig-label">Issued By</div>
        <div class="sig-line">
            <div class="sig-name">{{senderName}}</div>
            <div class="sig-role">{{#if senderDesignation}}{{senderDesignation}}{{else}}Advocate{{/if}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cc-section">
        <strong>CC:</strong> Copy retained for record and evidence purposes.
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is a legal document. {{#if companyName}}{{companyName}} — {{/if}}Legal Document System</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>